---
// Lead magnet banner — links to /guia page
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16 reveal" aria-label="Guia gratuito do viajante">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <a
      href="/guia"
      class="block glass-card glass-card-hover rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 group"
      style="border-color: rgba(245,166,35,0.15); background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,166,35,0.04), rgba(0,212,170,0.02));"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6">
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(245,166,35,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(245,166,35,0.2);">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" style="color:#F5A623;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <!-- Text -->
        <div class="flex-1 text-center sm:text-left">
          <span class="badge badge-gold mb-2">GRÁTIS — 52 PÁGINAS</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-black mb-1" style="color:#F0F0F5;">
            O Guia que a Tua Agência Nunca Te Deu
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color:#8892A4;">
            Tudo o que precisas de saber para viajar melhor, mais barato e sem stress. Descarrega grátis.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow -->
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 hidden sm:block">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" style="color:#F5A623;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
